          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "fr",
            "value": "Tirage aléatoire (avec stratification) à partir de l'enquête de filtrage, dite \"Vie Quotidienne et Santé\" (VQS) qui a été adjointe au recensement de la population de mars 1999 Enfants internes des institutions relevant des annexes 24 Adultes handicapés accueillis en foyers d’hébergement, foyers de vie, MAS, FDT et structures expérimentales Personnes hospitalisés dans un établissement psychiatrique Personnes prises en charge dans des établissements en faveur des personnes âgées"
          },
          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Random selection (with stratification) based on the screening survey, which is called the \"Daily Life and Health\" (VQS), which was added to the March 1999 general census  Children admitted into institutions related to annexes 24 Handicapped adults accommodated in residential facilities, residential care homes, MAS, FDT and experimental structures  Individuals hospitalised in a psychiatric institution  Individuals treated in elder care institutions"
          },
